        </div>

        <h2>Exchange Maintenance Margin Rates</h2>
        <p>Each exchange sets its own maintenance margin requirements, which directly impact your liquidation price. These rates represent the minimum equity percentage you must maintain relative to your position size. Lower MMR means you can withstand larger price movements before liquidation.</p>

        <div class="table-responsive">
          <table>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Exchange</th>
                <th>Base MMR</th>
                <th>Tier System</th>
                <th>Liquidation Fee</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
